# Dropdown ‚Äî Visual Specification

## Architecture

All visual styling lives in `packages/css/src/dropdown.css` using `@apply` for structural utilities and raw CSS for transitions, animations, and theme overrides.

---

## Class Inventory

### Base

| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown` | Wrapper ‚Äî `flex flex-col gap-1 relative` |
| `.acko-dropdown-label` | Label ‚Äî typography tokens, `color: var(--color-text-default)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-required` | Required asterisk ‚Äî `color: var(--color-error)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger` | Trigger button ‚Äî `flex items-center justify-between w-full rounded-full` |
| `.acko-dropdown-value` | Selected value ‚Äî `flex-1 min-w-0 overflow-hidden text-overflow:ellipsis` |
| `.acko-dropdown-placeholder` | Placeholder text ‚Äî `color: var(--color-text-muted)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-chevron` | Chevron icon ‚Äî `shrink-0 flex items-center ml-2` |
| `.acko-dropdown-menu` | Dropdown menu ‚Äî `absolute list-none`, shadow, rounded, animated |
| `.acko-dropdown-option` | Single option ‚Äî `flex items-center gap-2 cursor-pointer` |
| `.acko-dropdown-search` | Search input inside menu ‚Äî `w-full rounded-full` |

### Sizes

| Class | Height | Padding | Font Size |
|---|---|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-sm` | `h-10` (var(--scale-40)) | `px-4` | `var(--font-body-sm-size)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-md` | `h-12` (var(--scale-48)) | `px-5` | `var(--font-body-md-size)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-lg` | `h-14` (var(--scale-56)) | `px-6` | `var(--font-body-lg-size)` |

### Variants

| Variant | Behavior |
|---|---|
| `single` | Select one option, menu closes on select |
| `multi` | Select multiple, shows tags with remove button |
| `searchable` | Adds search input at top of menu |
| `grouped` | Options grouped under headers |

### States

| Class | Effect |
|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-open` | Active/open ‚Äî `border-color: var(--color-primary); box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px var(--color-primary)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-error` | Error ‚Äî `border-color: var(--color-error)`, shake animation |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger-filled` | Has value ‚Äî `border-color: var(--color-border-strong)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-trigger:disabled` | Disabled ‚Äî `cursor-not-allowed`, `--color-text-disabled` colors |
| `.acko-dropdown-label-open` | Label when open ‚Äî `color: var(--color-primary)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-label-error` | Label on error ‚Äî `color: var(--color-error-text)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-option-focused` | Keyboard-focused ‚Äî `background-color: var(--color-input-option-hover)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-option-selected` | Selected ‚Äî `--color-input-option-selected-bg` bg, `--color-input-option-selected-text` text, `font-weight: 500` |
| `.acko-dropdown-option-disabled` | Disabled option ‚Äî `color: var(--color-text-muted); cursor-not-allowed` |

### Multi-select Tags

| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown-tags` | Container ‚Äî `flex flex-wrap gap: --scale-4` |
| `.acko-dropdown-tag` | Individual tag ‚Äî `inline-flex rounded-full`, `--color-primary-subtle` bg, `--color-primary-active` text |
| `.acko-dropdown-tag-remove` | Remove button ‚Äî `inline-flex bg-transparent`, hover opacity |

### Helper/Error Text

| Class | Color |
|---|---|
| `.acko-dropdown-helper-text` | `var(--color-text-muted)` |
| `.acko-dropdown-error-text` | `var(--color-error-text)` |

---

## Animations

| Keyframe | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `acko-dropdown-menu-enter` | Menu fade-in + translateY(var(--space-2) ‚Üí 0) over 150ms |
| `acko-dropdown-shake` | Error shake ‚Äî 300ms horizontal oscillation |

