## Tokens Used

| Token | Usage |
|---|---|
| `--color-input-border` | Default trigger border |
| `--color-surface` | Trigger and menu background |
| `--color-surface-raised` | Dark theme trigger bg |
| `--color-primary` | Open state border, chevron, focus ring |
| `--color-input-option-hover` | Option hover bg |
| `--color-input-option-selected-bg` | Selected option bg |
| `--color-input-option-selected-text` | Selected option text |
| `--color-primary-active` | Multi-select tag text |
| `--color-primary-subtle` | Multi-select tag bg |
| `--color-border-strong` | Hover and filled trigger border |
| `--color-text-strong` | Value and option text |
| `--color-text-muted` | Placeholder, helper text, chevron, disabled option |
| `--color-text-disabled` | Disabled trigger text |
| `--color-error` | Required asterisk |
| `--color-error-text` | Error label and text |
| `--color-disabled-bg` | Disabled trigger bg (dark) |
| `--shadow-dropdown` | Menu shadow |
| `--z-dropdown` | Menu z-index |
| `--radius-full` | Trigger and tag border-radius |
| `--radius-3xl` | Menu border-radius |
| `--radius-lg` | Option border-radius |
| `--ease-out-cubic` | Chevron rotation, menu animation |

---

## Dark Theme Overrides

Scoped under `[data-theme="dark"]`:
- Trigger: `--color-surface-raised` bg, `--color-input-border` border
- Error trigger: `--color-error-text` border
- Disabled trigger: `--color-disabled-bg` bg
- Menu: `--color-surface-raised` bg, `--color-border` border
- Search: `--color-surface` bg, `--color-border` border
